Titolo: LHX Attack Chopper

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: LHX Attack Chopper is a combat helicopter simulation game published by Electronic Arts in 1990. Development was led by Brent Iverson who later designed Chuck Yeager's Air Combat. The game was released for MS-DOS and ported to the Mega Drive/Genesis.

Genere: Vehicle simulation 

Valutazione: N/A
